platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fans of YouTube celebrity PewDiePie will have a blast playing as him and his friends in this retro-themed sidescroller. Sprinkled with funny dialogue and surprising twists, the game is as wonderfully manic and goofy as his legendary videos. In your inexplicable battle with an army of barrels, you’ll go everywhere from the superstar’s home to a freeway chase to a dogfight in the clouds—unlocking new attacks and battling fearsome bosses.
